DESCRIPTION:Think you’re hydrated? Think again. Most of us wait until we’r
 e thirsty to grab a drink\, but by then\, your body is already playing ca
 tch-up. Join us for an interactive session where we dive deep into the sc
 ience of fluids and the physical reality of staying fueled. Learn about t
 he signs and impacts of dehydration and explore ways to stay hydrated bey
 ond just water. \n\nHosted by: IU Student Health Center\n\nAdditional Inf
 ormation can be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12410349
