DESCRIPTION:Join the Union Board Spirit and Traditions for Little Little 4
 99! Little Little 499 is Union Board’s take on celebrating one of IU’s mo
 st loved traditions\, Little 500. Participate in a cool and fun tricycle 
 race\, open for all students to participate in. No prior training is requ
 ired and everyone is welcome to join. \nYou are required to sign up\, if 
 you are wanting to race\, in teams of 4 and enjoy IU Day with us by compe
 ting on a little race track with your friends or your club members. Get t
 he opportunity to win prizes and swag. There will be food trucks\, a rock
  wall\, and an inflatable obstacle course. RSVP NOW!\nAll Indiana Univers
 ity events\, groups\, activities\, and educational\, cultural\, and histo
 rical observances welcome all IU students and other members of the Indian
 a University community.\n\nHosted by: Indiana Memorial Union Board\, Indi
 ana University Student Foundation\n\nAdditional Information can be found 
 at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12410254
