DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Wellness Week with a refreshing spin at Pedal & Pour
 s.\nJoin us for a laid-back afternoon centered on movement\, hydration\, 
 and a little Hoosier nostalgia. We’ll be serving up ice-cold water (becau
 se wellness is the vibe) while we screen the classic cycling film Breakin
 g Away.\nWhether you’re a seasoned cyclist\, a casual rider\, or just her
 e for the good company\, this event is all about taking a pause\, filling
  your cup (literally)\, and enjoying a feel-good story about determinatio
 n\, friendship\, and chasing big dreams on two wheels.\nStop by\, grab a 
 pour\, settle in\, and coast into the afternoon with us.\n\nHosted by: Fi
 rst Year & Family Experience Programs\, Student Care and Resource Center\
 n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu
 /event/12246700
