DESCRIPTION:Drama & Dubbing Night is a creative performance event combinin
 g a short play and live dubbing performances.\nPart 1: Short Play – “Diff
 erent Species”A 30-minute original short play directed by Getty. The play
  explores relationships and perspectives across differences through drama
 tic storytelling.\nPart 2: Live Dubbing PerformancesOpen-format dubbing s
 howcase. Participants can perform voice-overs for scenes from films\, ani
 me\, games\, or other media of their own creation and edition. All langua
 ges are welcome. We provide basic microphones and technical support.\nThi
 s event encourages cross-cultural expression\, multilingual creativity\, 
 and collaborative performance. Open to all students.\n\nHosted by: Heping
  (Peace) Chinese Theater Club \n\nAdditional Information can be found at:
  https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12324697
