DESCRIPTION:Need to blow off some steam before midterms? Come out and supp
 ort IU Habitat for Humanity at our Car Smash Fundraiser!\nFor a small don
 ation\, you’ll get the chance to smash a car using provided tools and pro
 tective gear. All proceeds will go directly toward supporting Habitat for
  Humanity’s mission of building safe\, affordable housing for families in
  need.\nWhether you’re swinging for stress relief\, fun with friends\, or
  a good cause\, this is an event you won’t want to miss.\n We can’t wait 
 to see you there! 💙🔨\n\nHosted by: Habitat for Humanity at Indiana Univ
 ersity\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://beinvolved.indi
 ana.edu/event/12382135
