CATEGORIES:Social Event
DESCRIPTION:Join the Student Involvement and Leadership Center and Union B
 oard for our End-of-the-Year Celebration: April Showers Bring May Flowers
 ! \nWe’re turning Dunn Meadow into a springtime hangout with tie-dye\, bo
 uquet making\, coloring\, a photo booth\, and tons of other fun stations 
 to help you relax\, get creative\, and celebrate making it through the ye
 ar. Come make something cute\, snap some pics\, and soak up all the good 
 end-of-semester vibes!\n\nHosted by: Student Involvement and Leadership C
