DESCRIPTION:The goal of the event is to empower students to transform unus
 ed clothing into bold\, personalized streetwear while fostering creativit
 y\, sustainability\, and self-expression.\nThe event is a hands-on design
  experience where members take an old or unused t-shirt and turn it into 
 a custom\, wearable statement piece. Inspired by streetwear culture and D
 IY fashion\, this event gives students access to stencils\, airbrush tool
 s\, bleach dye techniques\, and fabric markers to completely reimagine th
 eir clothing. Whether members prefer minimal graphics or bold experimenta
 l designs\, the event encourages creative freedom while promoting sustain
 able fashion practices. No prior experience is required\; members are enc
 ouraged to bring a shirt and create a design that reflects their identity
 .\n\nHosted by: Fashion Forward at IU\n\nAdditional Information can be fo
 und at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12433523
DTEND:20260429T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260422T023824Z
DTSTART:20260428T220000Z
