DESCRIPTION:Join us for our annual Cream & Crimson Carnival on Friday May 
 1st from 6pm-12am at Showalter Fountain! This year will feature attractio
 ns\, fire performers\, food\, free games\, music\, prizes and more!\nAdmi
 ttance is free for all attendees! All attendees must check in and sign a 
 waiver. You can complete the waiver by RSVP yes to this event. Once you h
 ave RSVPd please save your confirmation as this will be needed at the doo
 r.\nAll attendees under the age of 17 must be accompanied by an adult at 
 all times and all attendees under 18 must have a parent/guardian present 
 to sign waiver. \n\nHosted by: IU Late Nite\, Indiana Memorial Union\, St
 udent Involvement and Leadership Center\n\nAdditional Information can be 
 found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12413225
