DESCRIPTION:Join A Kid Again for our biweekly meeting!\nA Kid Again IU is 
 one of three Collegiate Chapters that have been serving families for over
  25 years. A Kid Again gives families who have a child struggling with a 
 life-threatening diagnosis a chance to make unique memories through our f
 ree\, monthly Adventures and fun events organized by A Kid Again. As a co
 llegiate chapter\, our support comes in three ways: volunteering\, philan
 thropy\, and outreach. \nWe would absolutely love to have you join our or
 ganization and help us achieve our goals as a Collegiate Chapter and a Na
 tional Chapter!\n\nHosted by: A Kid Again IU\n\nAdditional Information ca
 n be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/11951976
